OL,3,CJersey hosts first British Sign
OL,4,CLanguage bingo night
OL,6,FJersey's dDeaf community came together
OL,7,Ffor the island's first British Sign
OL,8,FLanguage (BSL) Bingo Night.
OL,10,FThe event at Age Concern on Friday 21
OL,11,FMarch was part of 'British Sign
OL,12,FLanguage Week' which celebrates the
OL,13,Flanguage's use and recognition.
OL,15,FAttendees learnt how to sign numbers
OL,16,Ffrom 1 to 99 before playing rounds of
OL,17,Fbingo which were called out using BSL.
