OL,3,CJersey hosts first British Sign
OL,4,CLanguage bingo night
OL,6,FFor BSL Week, Jersey's government
OL,7,Fteams have also been in school
OL,8,Fassemblies to teach children about
OL,9,Fsigning; they also brought together
OL,10,Fdeaf and hard-of-hearing students from
OL,11,Fdifferent schools for an activities
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,14,FBen and Karen Turner brought their two
OL,15,Fhearing children to the bingo night to
OL,16,Fteach them more about using BSL.
