OL,6,FBen explains: "We are deaf parents. We
OL,7,Fhave two children who are hearing, My
OL,8,Fson Oliver signs a little bit and they
OL,9,Fneed to learn sign language because
OL,10,Fit's our home language."
OL,12,FWhat does 'dDeaf' mean?
OL,14,F'dDeaf' is a shorthand term for people
OL,15,Fwho are 'deaf' (diagnosed with hearing
OL,16,Fbelow the normal level) as well as
OL,17,Fmedically 'Deaf' (diagnosed with the
OL,18,Fcondition of deafness).
