OL,4,CLanguage bingo night
OL,6,FThe government's Hearing and Deaf
OL,7,FSupport Team hope events - like this
OL,8,Fone - can also teach hearing people
OL,9,Fhow to better communicate with the
OL,10,Fisland's dDeaf community.
OL,12,FEsther Tremeer is the Team's Manager
OL,13,Fand helps to teach the island's deaf
OL,14,Fand hard-of-hearing children.
OL,16,FShe explains: "You have your deaf
OL,17,Findividuals who do sign - that's their
OL,18,Ffirst language - but obviously we want
OL,19,Fmore people to be able to sign with
OL,20,Fthem and for them to feel not so
OL,21,Fisolated.
